1. Copy header files from omex\gen\src\ and omex\omn\src\ to genium\genium_oapi\src\nar\resources\noarch\include\genium
In these header files, Add "genium/" to other genium header file includes.  But leave other std include intact
Eg. Change:
#include "omni.h"
#include "oal_align_packed.h"
#include <stdint.h>
To:
#include "genium/omni.h"
#include "genium/oal_align_packed.h"
#include <stdint.h>		// no change

Add the following line to omniapi.h
#include "omni.h"

2. Copy and rename the following lib to genium\genium_<lib name>\src\nar\resources\aol\amd64-Windows-msvc\lib\:
oapi.lib -> genium_oapi-<version>.lib
oapimtdll.lib -> genium_oapimt-<version>.lib
Zlibstat.lib -> genium_zlibstat-<version>.lib
Zlibwapi.lib -> genium_zlibwapi-<version>.lib

3. Linux: Copy and rename libgenium_oapi.a to genium\genium_oapi\src\nar\resources\aol\amd64-Linux-gpp\lib\libgenium_oapi-<version>.a

4. mvn clean deploy

*** 1.0-dummy ***
5. mvn versions:set -DnewVersion=1.0-dummy
6. update all child pom.xml, comment out <configuration>...</configuration> in <artifactId>nar-maven-plugin</artifactId>
7. mvn clean deploy
8. mvn versions:revert